{"tid":30631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母，依家圖書館係咩地方？人人都用電話","createTime":"2016-12-09T08:57:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-07T06:21:19.000Z","uid":90,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"769559f37a3dd4844f65a19207c78a22a43900de","tid":30631,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T08:57:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 影相/cut 圖啲聲都算，我忍到<br />\n同埋都叫理解到，可能呢頁你想分享比人<br />\n或者記低，但係可唔可以較靜音？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最想屌都係電話響<br />\n可唔可以較撚返靜音呢？<br />\n屌你老母，冇人想知你有電話<br />\n<br />\n最難譜都係接埋電話<br />\n你同人講講圖書館唔方便講嘢，我都接受同理解<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 吹埋水個堆係咩事？<br />\n真係唔屌唔化"},{"pid":"0ec9a2d8b321ac7cdbfb5007bff0e6877c2cc279","tid":30631,"uid":44584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-06T01:14:14.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"ebb1d1d4388ec9c22ce09bdd0b160ee5379cd29a","tid":30631,"uid":70596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-06T01:17:28.000Z","msg":"而家圖書館大部分都係掛著睇報章雜誌嘅廢老同霸位自修嘅大專生，真係有文化愛書嘅人少之又少"},{"pid":"d3ae8630f73689feffd3151279df9c51ef458976","tid":30631,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-06T01:29:52.000Z","msg":"圖書館=瘋人院"},{"pid":"0675a0c6fa7c1cf3f5a856eb62a8d962c654c76f","tid":30631,"uid":1589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-06T01:48:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>圖書館=瘋人院</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAgger <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bcb648fff96f0f687f9b54ddcda6488de1dabc9","tid":30631,"uid":36857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201